(49, 'Crowne Plaza West Cairo Arkan', 'Part of the iconic landmark, Arkan Plaza, Crowne Plaza West Cairo ??Arkan brings 178 modern guest rooms and suites to discerning business and leisure travelers alike, along with diversified dining options, state of the art meeting facilities and flexible event spaces. Taking you on a journey along the Mediterranean coast, the all-day dining restaurant, Amphora, serves an impressive selection of delicious dishes infused with tantalizing flavors and features a spacious terrace with direct access to Arkan Plaza. Mayrig offers vibrant Armenian recipes blended with silk road spices and Miss Li Lee?? offers exquisite Pan-Asian favorites and signature cocktails, which you can enjoy as you take in the spectacular views of the city from Miss Li Lee?? outdoor terrace. During your stay, enjoy free access to the award-winning LA7 gym or opt for a relaxing day by our rooftop infinity pool.Lying in close proximity to the Giza Pyramids Plateau and the Grand Egyptian Museum, the hotel?? prime location offers ample entertainment opportunities, a large auditorium and high end retail options, catering to your every need.', 'Arkan Plaza Zayed Entrance, 2 26th of July Corridor, First,Sheikh Zayed City,Giza Governorate,Egypt', 'book@serenitypines.com', 1, '5', '+20 12 3344 5566', 3, '\"[\\\"Free breakfast\\\",\\\"Free Wi-Fi\\\",\\\"Free parking\\\",\\\"Air conditioning\\\",\\\"Restaurant\\\",\\\"Full-service laundry\\\"]\"', '2025-05-23 02:59:03', '2025-05-23 02:59:03'),
