(89, 'Sun City Hotel - the Gabriel', 'Located in Cairo (Heliopolis), Sun City Hotel - The Gabriel is within a 15-minute drive of City Stars and Cairo International Stadium. This luxury hotel is 7 mi (11.2 km) from Virgin Mary\'s Tree and 9.7 mi (15.6 km) from Al-Azhar Park. Don\'t miss out on recreational opportunities including a health club and an outdoor pool. This Mediterranean hotel also features complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and gift shops/newsstands. Enjoy French cuisine at SALT RESTAURANT, one of the hotel\'s 2 restaurants, or stay in and take advantage of the 24-hour room service. Relax with a refreshing drink at one of the 2 bars/lounges. Cooked-to-order breakfasts are available daily for a fee. Featured amenities include limo/town car service, express check-in, and express check-out. Guests may use a train station pick-up service for a surcharge, and free self parking is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 25 individually decorated guestrooms, featuring iPod docking stations and DVD players. Your bed comes with down comforters and Egyptian cotton sheets. LED televisions with satellite programming provide entertainment, while complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected. Private bathrooms with shower/tub combinations feature jetted bathtubs and rainfall showerheads.', 'Suncity Mall, Autostrad Road,Cairo,Cairo Governorate,Egypt', 'service@sunshineridge.com', 1, '5', '+20 12 3435 5657', 3, '\"[\\\"Free breakfast\\\",\\\"Free Wi-Fi\\\",\\\"Free parking\\\",\\\"Air conditioning\\\",\\\"Restaurant\\\",\\\"Full-service laundry\\\"]\"', '2025-05-23 03:02:17', '2025-05-23 03:02:17'),
